# OpenCode config is fully generated by etc/sync-opencode.sh from dotfiles SSOT.
# /.config/opencode/ stays excluded by the wildcard rule above (no negation).
# Codex config.toml is generated by etc/sync-codex.sh and embeds a machine-specific
# absolute hook path ($DOT_DIR). Committing it makes Mac/Linux ping-pong, so it is
# generated per-machine (bootstrapped by install.sh). SSOT is .codex/config.base.toml.
/.codex/config.toml
